-- Spain to Present Eurogroup With EU15Bln Budget Cuts, ABC Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-03-01T08:54:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-01/spain-to-present-eurogroup-with-eu15bln-budget-cuts-abc-says.html
Economy Minister Luis de Guindos
will present a plan to cut  Spain ’s budget by 15 billion euros
($20 billion) to the eurogroup today,  ABC  reports, without
saying how it obtained the information.  The budget measures would reduce Spain’s deficit to 5.4
percent or 5.5 percent of gross domestic product this year, the
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Angeline Benoit in Madrid at 
